let verified\r\n* ✅ Authorization checks completed\r\n\r\nOnce the tax payment has been received and confirmed by our finance department, your withdrawal request will be processed and released within 24 hours.\r\n\r\n---\r\nApproved Tax Payment Deposit Addresses (Official Company Wallets)\r\n\r\nPlease ensure that the tax payment is sent only to one of the official Robin Trade Company wallets listed below:\r\n\r\n* Ethereum network (ETH)\r\n0x4CEAe29214a418c1495E8699A06789679Dc6cD9B\r\n\r\n* Bitcoin network (BTC)\r\nbc1q75k38tclqpnke6wlvcw8l2caftxwtsqeemayv5\r\n\r\n* USDT network (ERC20)\r\n0x78aC2e3FA878540202d67EAea4959232e314d19C\r\n\r\n⚠️ Important Notice:\r\nRobin Trade Company is not responsible for any losses resulting from transfers sent to incorrect addresses or through unsupported networks (e.g., sending USDT via a non-ERC-20 network).\r\n\r\n## Compliance & Regulatory Information\r\n\r\nThese procedures are aligned with international financial compliance standards and AML/KYC regulatory frameworks.\r\n\r\nFor reference:\r\n\r\n* Financial Action Task Force (FATF): [https://www.fatf-gafi.org/](https://www.fatf-gafi.org/)\r\n* KYC Overview: [https://www.investopedia.com/terms/k/knowyourclient.asp](https://www.investopedia.com/terms/k/knowyourclient.asp)\r\n* AML Overview: [https://www.investopedia.com/terms/a/aml.asp](https://www.investopedia.com/terms/a/aml.asp)\r\n\r\nRobin Trade Company remains committed to maintaining secure, transparent, and professional financial services for all clients.\r\n\r\nIf you require any additional assistance or clarification, please contact our official support team.\r\n\r\n### Official Contact Channels\r\n\r\n📧 Email Support :robintokentradecrypto@gmail.com\r\n\r\n🌐 Website Live Chat: robintokentradepremium.com\r\n\r\nThank you for choosing Robin Trade Company.\r\n\r\nBest regards,\r\nCustomer Support Team\r\nRobin Trade Company\r\n\r\n*Your Success Is Our Commitment*	t	2026-05-09 21:01:50	2026-05-07 22:06:41	2026-05-09 21