4	228	151	Trading Activity Verification Required – Account Temporarily Suspended (UID: 46221429)	Dear Mr. Roland Aouad\r\nUID: 46221429\r\n\r\nWe are writing to you regarding a review of your trading activity on our platform. Our system has identified a high volume of trading associated with your account, and as part of our ongoing commitment to security and regulatory compliance, we require additional verification to confirm the legitimacy of these trades. This is a standard procedure for accounts exhibiting similar trading patterns, ensuring that all activity is conducted by real individuals and not automated systems (bots).\r\n\r\nYour trading account has been temporarily frozen due to this review.\r\n\r\nWe appreciate your success in accumulating a total amount of  46,709.09 USDT. To verify that these trades were executed by you personally, we require a one-time verification deposit of 20% of your total profit, which amounts to  9,341.818  USDT. This deposit will be held securely in your trading account and will be added it to your account after successful verification.  Your account will be unfrozen and access restored immediately after the verification deposit is received and confirmed. Until then we restricted you to trade or withdraw.\r\n\r\nThis verification process is essential for us to confirm the legitimacy of your trading activity and maintain a fair and secure trading environment for all our users. Once the verification deposit is received, we will conduct a review of your trading patterns. Upon successful verification, your deposit will be returned to your trading account, and you can continue trading as usual.\r\n\r\nShould the verification process reveal any discrepancies or the use of automated trading tools, the deposit may be subject to forfeiture as per our terms and conditions.\r\n\r\nYou have 7 days from the date of this email to complete this verification process and make the required deposit. Failure to do so within this time frame will result in a penalty of 4% deduction from your trading capital of the required verification deposit being applied to your account for each subsequent day until the deposit is received.\r\n\r\nTo initiate the verification process, please make the 9,341.818 USDT deposit to your trading account. Once you have made the deposit, please reply to this email or you can reply to us through the customer service of your trading platform with the transaction details so we can promptly begin the verification process.\r\nNote: During the temporary suspension of your account, you cannot trade and also cannot withdraw during this time.	t	2026-06-05 22:16:04	2026-06-05 22:04:30	2026-06-05 22:16:04	\N
