ny is not responsible for any losses resulting from transfers sent to incorrect addresses or through unsupported networks (e.g., sending USDT via a non-ERC-20 network).\n\n---\n\n## Next Steps\n\nUpon successful receipt and blockchain confirmation of the tax payment, your withdrawal request will be released and processed to the Bitcoin address you provided.\n\n---\n\n📞 Official Contact Channels  \nFor your security, please communicate only through our verified channels:\n\n📧 Email: robintokentradecrypto@gmail.com  \n🌐 Website (Live Chat): www.robintokentradepremium.com\n\nThank you for choosing Robin Trade Company. We appreciate your cooperation and remain committed to providing secure, transparent, and professional financial services.\n\nWarm regards,  \nCustomer Support Team  \nRobin Trade Company\n\n*Your success is our commitment.	t	[]	2026-02-06 02:06:26	2026-02-11 11:15:29
